INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (24684,1,'2018-03-29 14:29:05','0000-00-00 00:00:00','<p>\n<strong>Help us improve WPForms</strong><br />\nWe&#8217;re celebrating WPForms&#8217; 2nd birthday. Since the launch of WPForms two years ago, it is now being used by over 900,000 websites. As we plan for the next three years, we need your feedback &#8211; it&#8217;ll take less than 90 seconds.\n</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wpforms.com/wpforms-nps-survey-2018/?utm_source=wpdashboard&#038;utm_medium=amnotification&#038;utm_campaign=npssurvey\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"button button-primary\">Share your feedback and help improve WPForms &raquo;</a> <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/wpforms-turns-2-years-old-whats-new-whats-coming-next/?utm_source=wpdashboard&#038;utm_medium=amnotification&#038;utm_campaign=npssurvey\" class=\"button button-secondary\" target=\"_blank\">Read our Annual Recap to See What&#8217;s New in WPForms</a></p>\n<p>Thanks as always for your continuous support of WPForms!<br />\nSyed Balkhi<br />\nFounder of WPForms<br />\nP.S. there&#8217;s a limited time 30% off coupon at the end of the survey :)</p>\n','','','draft','closed','closed','','','','','2018-03-29 14:29:05','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'http://e3d.seolocalservices.co/?post_type=amn_wpforms-lite&p=24684',0,'amn_wpforms-lite','',0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (24906,1,'2018-04-06 05:43:51','2018-04-06 05:43:51','[et_pb_section bb_built=\"1\" admin_label=\"Process\" _builder_version=\"3.0.106\" custom_padding=\"100px|0px|0px|0px\" box_shadow_style=\"preset7\" box_shadow_horizontal=\"0px\" box_shadow_vertical=\"-80px\" box_shadow_color=\"#ffffff\" prev_background_color=\"#000000\" template_type=\"section\"][et_pb_row custom_padding=\"27px|0px|27px|0px\" _builder_version=\"3.0.106\" locked=\"off\"][et_pb_column type=\"4_4\"][et_pb_text background_layout=\"dark\" _builder_version=\"3.0.106\" text_font=\"Open Sans||||||||\" text_text_color=\"#fdd13f\" header_text_align=\"center\" header_text_color=\"#fdd13f\" header_2_font=\"Open Sans|700|||||||\" header_2_font_size=\"38px\" header_2_letter_spacing=\"1px\" header_2_line_height=\"1.4em\" header_3_font=\"Poppins|700||on|||||\" header_3_font_size=\"14px\" header_3_text_color=\"#edbb5f\" header_3_letter_spacing=\"1px\" header_3_line_height=\"2em\" text_orientation=\"center\" max_width=\"700px\" module_alignment=\"center\" locked=\"off\"]\n\n<h2>OUR PROCESS</h2>\n\n[/et_pb_text][et_pb_divider color=\"#fdd13f\" show_divider=\"on\" divider_weight=\"2px\" height=\"2px\" _builder_version=\"3.0.106\" max_width=\"60px\" module_alignment=\"center\" locked=\"off\" /][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row _builder_version=\"3.0.47\" background_size=\"initial\" background_position=\"top_left\" background_repeat=\"repeat\"][et_pb_column type=\"4_4\"][et_pb_blurb title=\"Turn Your Brand Into An Experience\" use_icon=\"on\" font_icon=\"%%283%%\" icon_color=\"#ffffff\" use_circle=\"on\" icon_placement=\"left\" content_max_width=\"1100px\" use_icon_font_size=\"on\" icon_font_size=\"32px\" content_max_width_last_edited=\"off|\" _builder_version=\"3.0.106\" header_font=\"|700||on|||||\" header_font_size=\"14px\" header_letter_spacing=\"1px\" header_line_height=\"1.8em\" body_text_align=\"left\" body_letter_spacing=\"1px\" body_line_height=\"1.8em\" background_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style_all=\"dashed\" custom_margin=\"40px||40px|\" custom_padding=\"60px|30px|60px|30px\" animation_style=\"slide\" animation_direction=\"top\" animation_intensity_slide=\"10%\" animation=\"off\" box_shadow_style=\"preset3\" box_shadow_vertical=\"15px\" box_shadow_blur=\"80px\" box_shadow_color=\"rgba(0,0,0,0.2)\"]\n\nOur creative team is constantly in pursuit of new ways to create, scouring the market for trends and competitive insights. Using insights from our first conversation as well as our own market research, we propel our customers forward in the era of fast-paced change with forward-thinking. Adapting a unique mixture of materials and technology, we present design solutions that will make you standout. And we revise our designs with your feedback until we have it right.\n\n[/et_pb_blurb][et_pb_blurb title=\"Design Comes To Life\" use_icon=\"on\" font_icon=\"%%283%%\" icon_color=\"#ffffff\" use_circle=\"on\" icon_placement=\"left\" content_max_width=\"1100px\" use_icon_font_size=\"on\" icon_font_size=\"32px\" content_max_width_last_edited=\"off|\" _builder_version=\"3.0.106\" header_font=\"|700||on|||||\" header_font_size=\"14px\" header_letter_spacing=\"1px\" header_line_height=\"1.8em\" body_text_align=\"left\" body_letter_spacing=\"1px\" body_line_height=\"1.8em\" background_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style_all=\"dashed\" custom_margin=\"40px||40px|\" custom_padding=\"60px|30px|60px|30px\" animation_style=\"slide\" animation_direction=\"top\" animation_intensity_slide=\"10%\" animation=\"off\" box_shadow_style=\"preset3\" box_shadow_vertical=\"15px\" box_shadow_blur=\"80px\" box_shadow_color=\"rgba(0,0,0,0.2)\"]\n\nEvery project is engineered for efficiency and agility and built with precise, high-quality craftsmanship. Not one project leaves our facility without passing multiple quality checkpoints. Seamlessly integrated into the process, our logistics team synchronizes delivery and set-up. Every piece arrives on-site ready for installation, maximizing every minute (and dollar) spent onsite.\n\n[/et_pb_blurb][et_pb_blurb title=\"Make Lasting Impressions\" use_icon=\"on\" font_icon=\"%%283%%\" icon_color=\"#ffffff\" use_circle=\"on\" icon_placement=\"left\" content_max_width=\"1100px\" use_icon_font_size=\"on\" icon_font_size=\"32px\" content_max_width_last_edited=\"off|\" _builder_version=\"3.0.106\" header_font=\"|700||on|||||\" header_font_size=\"14px\" header_letter_spacing=\"1px\" header_line_height=\"1.8em\" body_text_align=\"left\" body_letter_spacing=\"1px\" body_line_height=\"1.8em\" background_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style_all=\"dashed\" custom_margin=\"40px||40px|\" custom_padding=\"60px|30px|60px|30px\" animation_style=\"slide\" animation_direction=\"top\" animation_intensity_slide=\"10%\" animation=\"off\" box_shadow_style=\"preset3\" box_shadow_vertical=\"15px\" box_shadow_blur=\"80px\" box_shadow_color=\"rgba(0,0,0,0.2)\"]\n\nEngage your audience with on-site and post-production media. We develop interactive content that captures attention and draws your audience into your environment and your story. Measuring the success and reach of our installations, we have found that adding media increases impressions and drives leads. Post-production photos and videos allow you to showcase your investment beyond installation, keeping your momentum going.\n\n[/et_pb_blurb][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section]','Our Process','','publish','closed','closed','','our-process','','','2018-04-23 03:23:40','2018-04-23 03:23:40','',0,'http://e3d.seolocalservices.co/et_pb_layout/our-process/',0,'et_pb_layout','',0);
